{"tid":1824031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭基煇倡減單程證限額 新地：純屬個人身份觀點","createTime":"2020-01-14T06:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T07:12:09.000Z","uid":13268,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2192c1759a0af3e982619da3cd28580d85a2dcc1","tid":1824031,"uid":13268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:56:47.000Z","msg":"有報道指，廣東省政協常委、新地執行董事郭基煇在廣東省政協十二屆三次會議上，提出將單程證上限由每日150個削減至75個。新鴻基地產表示，有關削減單程證人數上限的建議，純屬郭基煇日前以個人身份提出的觀點，集團並未曾就相關政策進行研究，尊重現行相關制度安排由兩地政府按政策需要決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />瘋狂割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01ffb92ed6574e5d139a56bb3f609308851e9f0","tid":1824031,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:05:50.000Z","msg":"你只不過係豬欄入面一隻肥d既豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6d379493b66ec3b176c15798c9572e3fef87da","tid":1824031,"uid":13268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a01ffb92ed6574e5d139a56bb3f609308851e9f0","tid":1824031,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:05:50.000Z","msg":"你只不過係豬欄入面一隻肥d既豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:12:09.000Z","msg":"等分豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}